{"type": "article", "id": 58327, "title": "Human Made 和肯德基联名正式公布，闲鱼开了家“吃土”甜品店 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人的一切", "date": "2018-11-15T06:19:07Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 925, "name": "圣诞节"}, {"id": 1941, "name": "肯德基"}, {"id": 43767, "name": "Human Made"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 1480589, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 29, "image": "img/article/article_show/201811151237073FW6yIADmCgVxMTP.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">又是跨界</h3><p line=\"p5UG\"><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/Bp66mPIg6Kt/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>HUMAN MADE 与 KFC 的联名系列正式公布。</b></a>该系列以 “HUMAN MADE Original Recipe” 为主题，并融合了 KFC 标志性的红、白、黑色调与“上校”图案，包括外套、T-Shirt、连帽衫、Tote Bag 和帽款等。将于 11 月 23 日开始在 HBX 及东京 HUMAN MADE 门店发售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181115123806fq3t9BapGjLEK0ne.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498829\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201811151238201xnfKzSYBuZUqMlR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498829\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181115123832mPoyxH9hD47YMSij.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498829\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><h3>值得一看的 Case</h3><p line=\"xh6e\">双 11 结束，<b><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/2191744334/4306231763740158\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">闲鱼在上海开了家官方指定吃土店“土其林餐厅”</a>，</b>供应多款表达吃土族心理的土味甜品。甜品和文案都很形象，“看完账单倒吸一口冷气的雪域土”是开心果树莓慕斯，配文则是“我，一个冷酷无情的人”。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181115123901X81xyHFTRA40ldeK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.877419\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201811151240027JAv2oX1z89brqFO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018111512392904Gsv7CMtZBh2mgc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181115123950DEAzNRnVh7qQeSKv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181115123915Nznkt1D2U3LFXK8i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><p line=\"Ofsg\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4306056336978829?wm=3333_2001&amp;sourcetype=weixin&amp;featurecode=newtitle&amp;from=timeline&amp;isappinstalled=0\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>淘宝昨天发布了一支预热双 12 的广告片 “1212 宝贝总决选”。</b></a>片中展现了每件商品“出道”之前的成长过程。其中，猪猪的参赛宣言是“成为最美味的火腿”。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=w0792r0g6x9\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"UOhS\"><b>新西兰航空拍了个飞行安全视频“嘻游新西兰”</b>。由曾参演”死侍2“ 的童星朱利安·迪尼森 (Julian Dennison) 主演，带领众多参演人员，通过轻松活力的说唱在新西兰各地宣传乘机安全须知。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=a07858wmnam\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"iHi4\">为配合此次视频的发布，新西兰航空机上杂志 “Kia Ora” 还推出了 6 组风格不同以往的封面大片。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181115124134L6zp30gKHJCUEt5v.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.843750\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"aU4a\">麦当劳法国为纪念巨无霸诞生 50 周年，<a href=\"https://www.thedrum.com/news/2018/11/14/mcdonald-s-big-mac-turns-50-en-france-with-endearingly-cheesy-retro-campaign\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>发起了一项复古海报 campaign。</b></a>该活动每张海报的画面中心都是巨无霸，设计风格运用了过去几十年里的流行风潮，发型、妆容、服饰乃至拍照 pose 都充满复古气息。意在表达无论其他怎么改变，巨无霸是不会变的。由 TBWA\\Paris 出品。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181115124446ftOIX05uRAbJm1p8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.491667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181115124241yqzvpmP2H7hCU8fl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.462810\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181115124258wno83vrZCGzV7Tqh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.477344\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181115124316gOPRAbo6r18sjFBV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.477344\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HpSnkU6ggCU\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>瑞典百货商场 Manor 今年的圣诞动画依然是上一年的小男孩，</b></a> 讲述了一个内心戏丰富的精灵成为小男孩圣诞礼物的故事。由 BETC 出品。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=v0793mmtmmh\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><h3>其他，也挺重要</h3><p line=\"KwaF\"><a href=\"https://www.thedrum.com/news/2018/11/14/uk-christmas-ad-spend-hits-new-high-thanks-online-investment\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>英国圣诞节电视广告支出预计会在本季度下降 4400 万英镑，</b></a>不过根据广告协会和 Warc 公布的数据显示，广告商会重新评估这部分，投放到在线媒体，Facebook、Google 和 YouTube 会是最大受益者。</p><p line=\"yTbm\">今年英国广告支出将会创造历史新高，预计有 64 亿英镑，比去年同期增加了 3 亿英镑。电视支出放缓，数字媒体支出将在圣诞节期间增长 12%，至 35 亿英镑，相比去年增加了 9000 万英镑。</p><p line=\"yTbm\" class=\"\">题图来自：<a href=\"&lt;iframe frameborder=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=a07858wmnam&quot; allowFullScreen=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;\" rel=\"nofollow\">HBX</a></p>"}